[Groovy] Class ProcessNodeDefController

      • ProcessNodeDefController

      • ProcessNodeDefinition controller class is used for managing node definitions in Process Editor. It is possible to create/change/delete definition, add custom pages for 'Wait' nodes, define variables visibility.

        Authors:
        Stephan Albers
        July Karpey
